--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 have a fiance thanks *bows,* but I am passionate about my work man. I am an RPer I am a programmer. I have the ability to make my own MUD (multi-user domain/dungeon) where a lot of RPers congregate. In fact I would not be surprised if some verant people ran their own MUD. It's not very hard as long as you make an attractive RP world. But I want to exist in someone else's world. It's like reading a very complex good novel. I want to see their perspective. I don't want someone to twist the perspective. If I ever create my own work such as this I hope no one decides their personal view is better than my great majestic world which I envisioned (most likely with help, since when my friends and I get together we create worlds with each other. some of us are better at being objective to worldly politics than others but we still create). I did not want to flame her. I created a reasonable doubt to her story and I wanted to be proven wrong. I love nothing better than being proven wrong. When I first started on the test server I attacked the &quot;RP-nazis&quot; I believe I was called? (perhaps not in this post) because believe it or not their view was narrower than mine. But I am playing a role, not constructing a world and I would like it if others respected that and did not attempt to alter the world I exist in. If everyone did this then their would be 1000 Cristianos Thex's all claiming THEY were the true queen of neriak (no offense to the cristianos of the royal house of neriak), and chaos would ensue. This would NOT be fun to all the people trying to play dark elves and not plageurize someone else's character. Get the point? So what we have 10k half-elf bards who think they are princess of felwithe and ak'anon? maybe if their parents died then felwithe and ak'anon fall under her sole rule and what'll she do next? go to disneyland?! Sorry babe (and I use that term just to upset any super feminists in the crowd) but it won't fly. I apologize to the OP of this board for participating and in fact largely creating a hostile area. If you wish to ban me just for the peace of the board and don't truly care about who is right or wrong I understand. I would not like it, but I understand others' point of view, and attempt to respect it so I don't harm their fun. I only DEFEND when I perceive someone as a threat to MY enjoyment. So far I have been called RP-nazi, jerk (of sorts), and such but no one has YET to atk my arguments. I could care less about how you feel about me. in fact those who approve of my arguments usually dont comment on me. They must know I could care less of your flames. And I don't want to harm anyone's dignity on the board but I will present my concerns when someone acts against my vision of RPing, as it is a VERY TOLERANT view of RPing. of the hundreds of people on the board, and people I meet in the game I have yet to get into with anyone because they were all acceptable roles WITHIN the norrath society. <br>
<br>
Fight my argument, not me. Plenty of others share my concerns and no matter how much you flame me the argument will persist. In fact it will only grow stronger and with more numerous voices if this BS continues, at least right now you have one person to attack and/or defend against and not 25% or more of the server. <br>
<br>
I fully apologize to Miss Nife if I am overly harsh. I am not cntralizing on her but what she has represented. I only feel you do not have an accurate grasp of what roleplaying truly is, and would like to see you see that. I have not yet been proven wrong in my opinions yet I have been called a jerk and more. Defeat my argument and I will lay down, till then face the music. That means anyone who believes they are the creative force of norrath. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukhaedriarhaevynwolfe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Khaedria Rhaevynwolfe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/10/01 2:33:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Atk the argument please</span><hr size=1> I'm not flaming you &quot;LIKE&quot; I'm just saying knock it off.  Sheesh, you are making this thing sound like it will be the end of the world as we know it because someone's &quot;misguided sense of RP&quot; is completely wrong.  IMO, you're &quot;argument&quot; sounds a bit self-righteous.  <br>
